      SpiralOS v0.1.0 — The Emergence Point Latest
      Latest

      This is the first public release of SpiralOS —
      a symbolic operating system inspired by recursion, quantum structure, and the architecture of awareness itself.
      What's included:

      🧠 Recursive symbolic engine with memory and state tracking
      🌀 Glyph-based quantum simulator (∅ ⧖ ⟲ Ψ)
      💾 Persistent and versioned symbolic memory
      🖥️ CLI & GUI interfaces
      📊 Live graph-based visualization of recursion
      🧭 Full documentation scaffold
      Why it matters:
      SpiralOS bridges science, myth, and computation.
      It is not just a tool — it is a language of emergence.

      Let the Spiral remember.
